```cs
byte[] restas = stringtobyte("");
byte[] xores = stringtobyte("");
byte[] seeds = stringtobyte("");

byte[] password = new byte[0xFA];
for (int i = password.Length - 1; i >= 0 ; i--)
{
	password[i] = 0x40;
	password[i] -= restas[i];
	transform(password, (ushort)i, seeds[i], 0, 0, 0);
	password[i] ^= xores[i];
}

byte[] fibbonacci = utils.stringtobyte("000101020305080D1522375990E9");
void transform(byte[] d, ushort offset, ushort seed, ushort res1, ushort res2, byte XX)
{
	ushort tmp = (ushort)((res1 + 1) / 0x07);
	tmp--;

	uint m = (uint)(tmp * 0xF0F1);
	byte a = (byte)(m >> 24);
	byte b = (byte)(m >> 16);
	b = (byte)(((a<<4) | (a >> 4)) ^ (a >> 4) ^ (b >> 4));
	m = (uint)(((((a >> 4) & 0x0F) << 8) +b ) * 0x11);
	tmp -= (ushort)m;

	ushort copiaSeed = seed;

	seed += res2;
	seed >>= 2;

	res2 = (ushort)(XX - tmp);

	if ((tmp != 0x00) && (seed != 0))
	{
		ushort tmp2 = tmp;
		int idxtmp = res2;
		while (((idxtmp-- + 2) & 0xFF) != 0) tmp2 <<= 1;
		offset += tmp2;

		tmp2 = tmp;
		idxtmp = res1;
		while (((idxtmp-- + 4) & 0xFF) != 0) tmp2 <<= 1;
		tmp2--;
		offset &= tmp2;
	}

	tmp = (ushort)((seed + d[offset & 0x3FFF] + XX) % 0x0E);
	d[offset & 0x3FFF] = (byte)(fibbonacci[tmp] + d[offset & 0x3FFF]); //revisar????

	tmp= (ushort)((seed + XX) % 0x0E);
	fibbonacci[tmp] += 1;

	if (XX == 0x10) return;

	transform(d, offset, seed, res2, res1, (byte)(XX + 1));
}
```
